data.description: This adorable Sun City gem is perfectly situated with amazing Golf Course VIEWS! This quaint home features a nice sized living room with tile flooring. The kitchen has been recently updated with granite counter tops, tile backsplash, cabinets PLUS a gas stove! All appliances included. This home does have a 1 car garage with additional parking. Plenty of storage space and a fenced yard! The roof was recently replaced in 2018 and a new Sewer line in 2014! All windows have been replaced as well as the furnace in 2013. There are solar tubes and extra insulation in the attic. The enclosed patio could be your perfect morning retreat or place to relax watching those beautiful AZ Sunsets!! Sun City is a wonderful over 55 age restricted community See it before it's gone!
